      <title>插件选项</title>
      <link>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/v1/copy-code/zh/config.html</link>
      <guid>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/v1/copy-code/zh/config.html</guid>
      <source url="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/v1/copy-code/rss.xml">插件选项</source>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Oct 2020 05:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="selector"> selector</h2>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>string | string[]</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>'.theme-default-content div[class*=&quot;language-&quot;] pre'</code></li>
</ul>
<p>代码块选择器</p>
<h2 id="duration"> duration</h2>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>number</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>2000</code></li>
</ul>
<p>提示消息显示时间，设置为 <code>0</code> 会禁用提示。</p>
<h2 id="showinmobile"> showInMobile</h2>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>boolean</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>false</code></li>
</ul>
<p>是否展示在移动端</p>
<h2 id="delay"> delay</h2>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>number</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>500</code></li>
</ul>
<p>注册复制按钮的延时，单位 ms。</p>
<p>如果你使用的主题有切换动画，建议配置此选项为 <code>切换动画时长 + 200</code></p>
<h2 id="pure"> pure</h2>
<ul>
<li>类型: <code>false</code></li>
<li>默认值: <code>false</code></li>
</ul>
<p>是否生成样式纯净的小而简单的复制按钮。</p>
<h2 id="locales"> locales</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>类型: <code>CopyCodeLocaleConfig</code></p>
<div><pre><code><span>interface</span> <span>CopyCodeLocaleData</span> <span>{</span>
  <span>/**
   * 复制按钮文字
   */</span>
  copy<span>:</span> <span>string</span><span>;</span>

  <span>/**
   * 复制成功提示消息文字
   */</span>
  hint<span>:</span> <span>string</span><span>;</span>
<span>}</span>

<span>interface</span> <span>CopyCodeLocaleConfig</span> <span>{</span>
  <span>[</span>localePath<span>:</span> <span>string</span><span>]</span><span>:</span> CopyCodeLocaleData<span>;</span>
<span>}</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br><span>12</span><br><span>13</span><br><span>14</span><br><span>15</span><br></div></div></li>
<li>
<p>必填: 否</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>复制按钮插件的国际化配置。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>指南</title>
      <link>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/v1/copy-code/zh/guide.html</link>
      <guid>https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/v1/copy-code/zh/guide.html</guid>
      <source url="https://vuepress-theme-hope.github.io/v1/copy-code/rss.xml">指南</source>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Oct 2020 05:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用"> 使用</h2>
<p>此插件会自动添加复制按钮到每个代码块的右下角。</p>
<p>默认情况下，按钮仅在桌面模式显示，如果你需要在移动端展示这个按钮，请将 <code>showInMobile</code> 设置为 <code>true</code>。</p>
<p>在用户点击复制按钮后，屏幕上会显示一个复制成功的提示。默认的提示时长为 2000ms，如果你需要更改这个时长，请设置 <code>duration</code>(单位 ms)，如果你不需要这个提示，请将 <code>duration</code> 设置为 <code>0</code>。</p>
<h2 id="演示"> 演示</h2>
<CodeGroup>
<CodeGroupItem title=" TS">
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.ts</span>
<span>export</span> <span>default</span> <span>{</span>
  plugins<span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"copy-code1"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// 插件选项</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
<CodeGroupItem title=" JS">
<div><pre><code><span>// .vuepress/config.js</span>
module<span>.</span>exports <span>=</span> <span>{</span>
  <span>plugins</span><span>:</span> <span>[</span>
    <span>[</span>
      <span>"copy-code1"</span><span>,</span>
      <span>{</span>
        <span>// 插件选项</span>
      <span>}</span><span>,</span>
    <span>]</span><span>,</span>
  <span>]</span><span>,</span>
<span>}</span><span>;</span>
</code></pre>
<div><span>1</span><br><span>2</span><br><span>3</span><br><span>4</span><br><span>5</span><br><span>6</span><br><span>7</span><br><span>8</span><br><span>9</span><br><span>10</span><br><span>11</span><br></div></div></CodeGroupItem>
</CodeGroup>
]]></content:encoded>
